ComicInfo.Summary: Opens with Gerard, an elf, in front of a university's council when an uprising ensues. Meanwhile, the Rat Queens are locked in cages on a frozen mountain top being prepared to be dinner for a goblin hoard. After eating Betty's poisoned candy, the Rat Queens escape the goblins, and continue their quest to find Hannah's father. They arrive in Dunlas, an arcane university town, only to discover it is mostly deserted. After running into an old friend, Polle, Hannah and the Rat Queens turn in for the night while Betty gets attacked by a cloaked halfing in her sleep.
ComicInfo.Title: Demons, Part One
ComicInfo.Writer: Kurtis J. Wiebe,Stjepan Šejić,Kurtis J. Wiebe
